The paper deals with the economics of the interaction between Mobile Virtual Network Operators (MVNOs) and Mobile Network Operators (MNOs), which involves game theory, network infrastructure, and communication engineering. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), followed by cs.NI (Computer Science and Networking), cs.IT (Computer Science and Information Theory), cs.CE (Computer Science and Computational Engineering), and cs.SI (Computer Science and Social and Information Networks).
